FINLAND: FINLAND BANK AUG DAILY LIQUIDITY NEED FIM 4.25 BLN.FINLAND BANK AUG DAILY LIQUIDITY NEED FIM 4.25 BLN.The Bank of Finland said onTuesday the required daily money market liquidity balance forthe rest of the month was 4.25 billion markka.The central bank gave the following figures (FIM mln): Liquidity estimate for August 22		   3,600 Minimum reserve requirement for Aug		6,445 Average reserves to August 19			7,852 Required daily balance for remaining period    4,254-- Helsinki newsroom, +358-0-680 50 245